description: A hearty fragrant stew with succulent venison chunks and plenty of seasonal veggies. This is comfort food at its finest and ideal for serving to family and friends.
name: Venison Stew Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 medium white onion, peeled and chopped

recipeInstructions.text: Heat up a large pan to a medium heat and then add the oil to the pan.
Pre-heat the oven to 180Â°C. Fry the onion & carrot for 4 minutes.
Add the diced venison and herbs to the pan and fry while mixing for a further 4 minutes.
Add the meat and veg to a large casserole dish and then add the rest of the ingredients and mix together well.
Place the oven and allow to cook for 150 minutes before serving.
